atio: 正常中位数0.0 → 故障中位数0.0，P99从0.0升至15.4，变化率200%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"paymentservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max和rrt指标出现严重性能退化，P99响应时间大幅增加\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max: 正常中位数2518.0 → 故障中位数2481.0，P99从3981.93升至54187.24，变化率172.62%；rrt: 正常中位数2200.5 → 故障中位数2308.62，P99从3369.75升至28504.95，变化率157.71%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-06\",\n      \"reason\": \"node_memory_usage_rate出现异常变化，内存使用率波动较大\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_memory_usage_rate: 正常中位数26.31 → 故障中位数20.19，P99从27.42升至56.27，变化率68.96%\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**分析要点**：\n1. **cartservice-0** 的错误率异常最为显著，error_ratio的P99变化率高达200%，表明该服务是故障的主要源头\n2. **paymentservice-2** 的响应时间严重退化，rrt_max的P99值从4秒激增到54秒，严重影响用户体验\n3. **aiops-k8s-06** 节点的内存使用率出现异常波动，虽然中位数下降，但P99值大幅上升，可能存在内存压力\n4. 需要进一步结合日志和链路追踪数据来确认cartservice-0的具体故障原因\n\n--- Trace Agent Findings ---\n基于采集到的链路追踪数据，我现在进行故障分析。让我分析这些异常调用边的延迟和错误模式。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->emailservice\", \n    \"checkoutservice->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->cartservice\",\n    \"cartservice->redis\",\n    \"frontend->shippingservice\",\n    \"frontend->productcatalogservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"checkoutservice内部调用异常严重：ShipOrder操作从12518ms激增至65958ms（5.3倍），EmptyCart从15802ms激增至84650ms（5.4倍），GetProduct从19533ms增至28131ms（1.4倍）\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"cartservice调用redis的HMSET操作从1573ms激增至10132ms（6.4倍），EmptyCart操作从2409ms增至12492ms（5.2倍）\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\", \n      \"evidence\": \"shippingservice的GetQuote操作从216ms增至1423ms（6.6倍），ShipOrder从226ms增至962ms（4.3倍），多个frontend调用也出现延迟\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 分析总结\n\n**主要发现：**\n1. **checkoutservice是核心瓶颈** - 多个内部操作出现严重延迟，特别是ShipOrder和EmptyCart操作\n2. **cartservice与redis交互异常** - HMSET操作延迟激增6.4倍，表明数据存储层存在问题\n3. **shippingservice响应缓慢** - GetQuote操作延迟增加6.6倍，影响结账流程\n\n**根因分析：**\n- 最下游的redis操作异常可能是根本原因，影响了cartservice\n- cartservice的异常进一步传播到checkoutservice\n- checkoutservice的延迟影响了整个结账流程，包括shipping和email服务\n\n**建议下一步：**\n- 检查redis集群的健康状态和性能指标\n- 验证cartservice与redis的连接稳定性\n- 分析checkoutservice的资源使用情况\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nNo consensus yet\n\n--- Metric Agent Findings ---\nSee Log Findings for Full Context\n\n--- Trace Agent Findings ---\nSee Log Findings for Full Context\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nDISAGREED\n================================\n请基于上述全量信息以及你的 Trace 数据，对当前故障进行分析。\n重点：请在返回 JSON 的 'stance' 字段中明确标记 'SUPPORT', 'OPPOSE' 或 'NEUTRAL'。", "raw_metric_result": {"status": "success", "message": "成功加载metric数据。UUID: 725d8034-130", "anomaly_metrics": "metric_type,service_name,pod_name,node_name,metric_name,normal_median,fault_median,normal_p99,fault_p99,median_change_ratio,p99_change_ratio\nservice,cartservice,cartservice-0,N/A,client_error_ratio,0.0,0.0,0.0,15.4,0.0,2.0\nservice,cartservice,cartservice-0,N/A,error_ratio,0.0,0.0,0.0,15.4,0.0,2.0\nservice,paymentservice,paymentservice-2,N/A,rrt_max,2518.0,2481.0,3981.93,54187.24,0.0148,1.7262\nservice,paymentservice,paymentservice-2,N/A,rrt,2200.5,2308.62,3369.75,28504.95,0.048,1.5771\npod,N/A,redis-cart-0,N/A,pod_cpu_usage,0.0,0.0,0.03,0.1,0.0,1.0418\nservice,currencyservice,currencyservice-0,N/A,rrt_max,4413.0,3742.0,17370.3,54748.35,0.1646,1.0366\nnode,N/A,N/A,aiops-k8s-06,node_memory_usage_rate,26.31,20.19,27.42,56.27,0.2632,0.6896\nservice,paymentservice,paymentservice-1,N/A,rrt_max,2452.5,2586.0,3692.02,6638.0,0.053,0.5704\nservice,paymentservice,paymentservice-1,N/A,rrt,2137.62,2213.0,2812.92,4735.61,0.0347,0.5094\nservice,emailservice,emailservice-0,N/A,rrt,1894.34,1930.84,2682.19,4419.35,0.0191,0.4892\nservice,emailservice,emailservice-0,N/A,rrt_max,3165.0,3291.5,6142.9,10066.24,0.0392,0